If you are a pizza a pizza lover, than trying pizza from A&S is a MUST. Excellent food, friendly staff and clean place. If you like Alfredo sauce, than slice of Chicken Alfredo pizza will make your day; if you are fan of Buffalo Wings, than go for Buffalo Chicken slice. If you prefer salads, than order delicious Caesar salad. Their Buffalo Wings are to die for! Complete your lunch or dinner with fresh fried zeppoles - which are delicious! If you are going to visit Staten Island, than please put lunch at A&S on your TO DO list :)
